27 baby!! 🥰 I’ll try to make this short and sweet, but birthdays can really make you do a lot of reflecting! (I’ve already cried once)! Today I could not be more grateful for this past year and where I am at now. Every high and low, the growth to get me here, every person in my life, including all of you!

node.text:
Happy July!! This month is extra special to me, not only because it’s my birthday month ☺️, BUT this month gives me the most kick off to summer vibesssss!
-
New goals, new month. Take one small step towards that monthly goal. MINE - be with Mother Nature more! SO everyday for me get outside one time - is a small realistic goal! Share one small goal below and write it at the top of your journal on a daily basis! ⬇️

node.text:
New week, here we go!! Your girl is practicing to keep my mind open to what lessons I need to listen for throughout my day. The more I ignore what my body is trying to tell me, the more I will feel disconnected to myself and almost that push and pull feel throughout my days! Anyone else? 
-
Also, with my resting I was listening to a lot of new podcasts! I will share some of my favorites in my stories. What are some of your favorite podcast?!

node.text:
Just finished filming some fun workouts for youuu, ah can’t wait to do them all together!! Now ready to eat some food and have a spicy margarita this weekend, anyone else? HAPPY FRIDAY FRIENDS! 
-
Also my girls, Click the link in my bio to join my Facebook group for fun bts and updates on the platform! I will share here too, but first looks on their 🥰!
